simphony.util.messages

Class MessageCenter

  • java.lang.Object
    • simphony.util.messages.MessageCenter

  • public class MessageCenter
extends java.lang.Object
    A class for handling all sorts of messages. This class receives messages of different levels through it's different methods and passes these messages on to it's listeners.

    To retrieve an instance of this class use getMessageCenter(Class) or getMessageCenter(Class, Map).

    Author:
    Jerry Vos
    See Also:
    getMessageCenter(Class), getMessageCenter(Class, Map), addMessageListener(MessageEventListener), removeMessageListener(MessageEventListener)
